{"tid":288243,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"流浪漢在街頭救了一隻貓，沒想到卻從此登上人生巔峰","createTime":"2017-06-18T05:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T08:55:34.000Z","uid":17738,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e28ef9b405c98ecaa0c979912a6dff75e4d4417","tid":288243,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/da9671786a14f1bd12d30e11035663cb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2Fda9671786a14f1bd12d30e11035663cb.jpeg&h=6d33e9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國倫敦的一條大街上，常常能看到一名流浪歌手帶著他的貓咪一同表演，表演完以後，他們還會擊掌鼓勵彼此。<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/326b09cfc6d879094b8209aed6c72195.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2F326b09cfc6d879094b8209aed6c72195.jpeg&h=b98f3fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子四處流浪，靠賣藝獻唱為生，居無定所。一次偶然，他在街上發現了一隻受了傷且餓得奄奄一息的貓咪，男子儘管沒什麼錢，可是還幫助了這隻貓咪，把它送到寵物醫院治療，還給它買來食物。<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/e40225bc83447f82475a801ccbb9fb55.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2Fe40225bc83447f82475a801ccbb9fb55.jpeg&h=140267c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子每天都是飽一頓餓一頓的，他也從沒想過養啥寵物，可沒想到自此後，這隻貓現卻賴上了他，不肯離開男子半步。<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/b0fc54e0c25a5e4d263b5087a7047d37.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2Fb0fc54e0c25a5e4d263b5087a7047d37.jpeg&h=6534e31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子不只窮困潦倒，還有毒癮、酗酒，日子過得是一團糟。可沒想到自從小貓跟著他以後，居然一點點地改變了男子。<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/4bd5a9040034e51664df6d3226599a53.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2F4bd5a9040034e51664df6d3226599a53.jpeg&h=2a3acdce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來男子開始嘗試創造新的音樂作品，慢慢的也有了人氣，也有一些音樂節請他做嘉賓，收入也比以前高多了，男子每次賣藝這隻貓都會在一旁陪著，卻無意間吸引了路人的極大關注和支援。<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/590f883402bf9fc816b91fcff4f931a9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2F590f883402bf9fc816b91fcff4f931a9.jpeg&h=55341274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n很多人對男子施以援手，還幫詹姆斯找了一個工作，能有一個棲息之所。現在男子在倫敦一家雜誌社做銷售，著堅持自己的音樂之路，男子還成功戒掉了毒癮、酒癮，這個奇特的組合在網路上爆紅。<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/fc51d66066c0975089a9e47de3ead7b5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2Ffc51d66066c0975089a9e47de3ead7b5.jpeg&h=a39a501f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子還依據和貓咪的這段故事寫出了暢銷書《一隻名叫鮑勃的漂泊貓》，收入很可觀。從一個無人知道的流浪漢，一個小偷小摸的癮君子，到現在受人喜歡的歌手，暢銷書作者，具有百萬粉絲的大V，男子說這一切都是貓咪帶來的，這不是一隻一般的貓，而是一個陪著他的天使。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gooread.com/article/20122668418/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gooread.com%2Farticle%2F20122668418%2F&d=Wds3u3a4smCxyBTkp6QeFZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=78a61cfb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gooread.com/article/20122668418/</a>"},{"pid":"a6f5c1f297170b3d78888306a0b3243506be7d08","tid":288243,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"戲都落埋喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c708d9694932adc7f3dc1eb1ce6fc1f5d21369","tid":288243,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"套戲幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f096fb2f9964cddd3223835f8f2bd76a851dfd","tid":288243,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戲都落埋喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a9caa1a636c806c397df7d13013c1e01ec5706","tid":288243,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐？"},{"pid":"54645ce20b5b5418dbc18f050a67083a83b334af","tid":288243,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套戲幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇完套戲真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}